query.pigql: q = load "ServiceAppointmentDemo"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('EarliestStartTime_Year','EarliestStartTime_Month','EarliestStartTime_Day')")}}; q = filter q by {{column(ServiceTerritoryId_1.result, ["ServiceTerritoryId"]).asEquality("ServiceTerritoryId")}}; q = filter q by {{column(NumberCompletedJobsByWorkType.selection, ["ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name"]).asEquality("ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name")}}; q = filter q by 'StatusCategory' == "Completed"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate count()/{{column(Time_Selection.selection, ["NumberOfDays"]).asObject()}} as avg_jobs_completed_by_day;

GrainTable.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceAppointmentDemo.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('EarliestStartTime_Year','EarliestStartTime_Month','EarliestStartTime_Day')")}}; q = filter q by {{column(ServiceTerritoryId_1.result, ["ServiceTerritoryId"]).asEquality("ServiceTerritoryId")}}; q = foreach q generate 'AppointmentNumber' as 'AppointmentNumber',  first('ParentRecordId_WorkOrderNumber') as 'ParentRecordId_WorkOrderNumber', first('ParentRecordId_AccountId_Name') as 'ParentRecordId_AccountId_Name'; q = order q by 'AppointmentNumber' asc;q = limit q 100;

query.pigql: a = load "ServiceAppointmentDemo"; a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('EarliestStartTime_Year','EarliestStartTime_Month','EarliestStartTime_Day')")}}; a = filter a by {{column(ServiceTerritoryId_1.result, ["ServiceTerritoryId"]).asEquality("ServiceTerritoryId")}}; a = filter a by {{column(NumberCompletedJobsByWorkType.selection, ["ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name"]).asEquality("ParentRecordId_WorkTypeId_Name")}}; sa = group a by 'Id'; sa = foreach sa generate sum('ActualDuration') as 'sum_ActualDuration', 'Id' as 'Id', first('ServiceTerritoryId_OperatingHoursId') as 'ServiceTerritoryId_OperatingHoursId';  ar = load "AssignedResourceDemo"; ar = cogroup ar by 'ServiceAppointmentId' inner, sa by 'Id'; ar = foreach ar generate sum(ar['ActualTravelTime']) as 'sum_ActualTravelTime', first(ar['ServiceResourceId']) as 'ServiceResourceId', first(sa['ServiceTerritoryId_OperatingHoursId']) as 'ServiceTerritoryId_OperatingHoursId'; ra = load "ResourceAbsenceDemo"; ra = cogroup ra by 'ResourceId' inner, ar by 'ServiceResourceId'; ra = foreach ra generate sum(ra['AbsenceMinutes']) as 'sum_AbsenceMinutes'; ts = load "TimeSlotDemo"; ts = cogroup ts by 'OperatingHoursId' inner, sa by 'ServiceTerritoryId_OperatingHoursId'; ts = foreach ts generate sum(ts['AvailableTime']) as 'sum_AvailableTime'; t = group a by 'AssignedResource_User_User_Name'; t = foreach t generate unique('AssignedResource_User_User_Name') as 'unique_AssignedResource_User_User_Name'; q = union sa,ar,ra,ts,t; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate coalesce(((sum('sum_ActualDuration') + sum('sum_ActualTravelTime')) / (sum('sum_AvailableTime') - sum('sum_AbsenceMinutes'))) / unique('unique_AssignedResource_User_User_Name'),0) as 'avg_util_rate';
